  },
  "excerpt": {
    "en": "How to structure payable cycles, approvals, and deductions so supplier settlement stays controlled and auditable.",
    "ar": "كيفية تنظيم دورات المستحقات والموافقات والخصومات بحيث تبقى تسويات الموردين منضبطة وقابلة للتدقيق."
  },
  "content": {
    "en": [
      {
        "_key": "set-en-01",
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "set-en-01-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Supplier settlement is not just a back-office task. It is one of the clearest tests of whether transport operations, approvals, and commercial terms are being managed in a disciplined way.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_key": "set-en-02",
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "set-en-02-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When cycles are unclear, every payment run turns into a negotiation. Teams spend time rebuilding service history, debating deductions, and checking which exceptions were actually approved.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_key": "set-en-03",
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "set-en-03-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Three settlement controls to define early",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_key": "set-en-04",
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1,
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "set-en-04-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Cycle cutoff dates linked to service periods and invoice submission rules.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_key": "set-en-05",
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1,
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "set-en-05-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Deduction logic tied to SLA, service failure, or compliance events.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_key": "set-en-06",
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1,
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "set-en-06-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A dispute and resubmission path that preserves the audit trail.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_key": "set-en-07",
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "set-en-07-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Well-designed settlement cycles protect margin, reduce payout friction, and give both buyers and operators a cleaner commercial relationship over time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "ar": [
      {
        "_key": "set-ar-01",
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "set-ar-01-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "تسوية الموردين ليست مهمة خلفية فقط، بل هي أحد أوضح الاختبارات على مدى انضباط التشغيل والموافقات والشروط التجارية في برنامج النقل.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_key": "set-ar-02",
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "set-ar-02-span",
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "عندما تكون الدورة غير واضحة، يتحول كل صرف إلى جولة تفاوض جديدة. وتضيع الفرق وقتها في إعادة بناء سجل الخدمة، ومناقشة الخصومات، والتحقق مما إذا كانت الاستثناءات قد اعتُمدت بالفعل.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
